{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_9", "eventName": "風暴瞭望", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "9-13", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "戰地救援", "storyInfo": "上校放號角離開，號角率隊員前去搶奪城郊通訊基地台。Outcast在交戰區發現了重傷並急性感染的深池“領袖”，力排眾議，前去救援。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G2_opera_room", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$batmeeting_intro", "key": "$batmeeting_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#7"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "漢密爾頓上校，我希望你明白自己都做了什麼。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#7"}, {"id": 11, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_227_1"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我做了什麼？我成功打擊了維多利亞的敵人，為我們贏來了難得的勝利。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#7"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你真以為你會贏？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#7"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_227_1"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原本佔領市政廳和其他重要設施的渣滓們都被清除了。你都聽到了，我們的士兵正在一點點奪回城市。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使事情真的如你所願，鬼魂部隊就此一蹶不振，你順利守住了小丘郡——", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#7"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也給維多利亞帶來了不可逆的損失！", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#7"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_227_1#6"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在說什麼鬼話？我知道了，你還在惦記著那些平民。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#6"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我再說一遍，斯卡曼德羅斯，這是一場戰爭，沒有什麼勝利是不流血的。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#6"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#7"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "少冠冕堂皇了，你的目標從來都是當地居民。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#7"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你命令炮兵營私藏軍火，暗中製造髒彈的時候，鬼魂部隊還沒進入小丘郡！", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#7"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_227_1"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你就是不肯善罷甘休是不是？", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_227_1#5"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了，反正事情很順利，你也沒什麼機會礙手礙腳了。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#5"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#7"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "順利？就因為你給眼前的戰火煽了風？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#7"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戰爭不是目的，而是手段。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#7"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們多年來拼命戰鬥，為的就是確保維多利亞的安全和穩固。而你呢？你只用了一個中午，就摧毀了無數人的努力。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#7"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你竟然以維多利亞軍隊的名義無差別地攻擊平民——無論那些人是什麼出身，他們在名義上都還是維多利亞公民。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#7"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_227_1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們把自己叫做塔拉人！", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們國家裡有多少塔拉人？十分之一，還是五分之一？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#7"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，你或許認為他們是少數。可這麼多人的仇恨一旦被點燃，足以徹底毀掉我們的國家！", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#7"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_227_1#5"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵，他們壓根不是維多利亞軍隊的對手。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#5"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#7"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們本來就不該成為我們的對手！", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#7"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看看你在讀的書，你尊崇著第一代阿斯蘭王的偉業，但你有沒有想過，是什麼讓來自異邦的阿斯蘭成為了維多利亞的王？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果阿斯蘭不是和德拉克簽訂了休戰條約，如果當年的德拉克蓋爾王沒有退讓並接受同族王室的決定，今天的維多利亞根本不會存在！", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#7"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你有什麼資格——只因為一己的仇恨和敵意，就將維多利亞再度拖至內戰邊緣？！", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#7"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_227_1"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯卡曼德羅斯，你當真相信你說的這些話嗎？", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你真的以為，我區區一個地方駐軍的指揮官，就能輕而易舉地決定維多利亞未來的走向？", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_227_1#5"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你有沒有想過，為什麼......倫蒂尼姆沒有聲音？", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#5"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_227_1#2"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我本可以殺了你，縱使你是貴族，倫蒂尼姆也不會為了一名喪生在叛軍炮火下的中尉而追究我的責任。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#2"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是我沒有。我尊重你對維多利亞的忠誠，我不忍看著所謂的人性鈍化維多利亞的利劍。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#2"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睜開眼睛看看吧，戰爭早就開始了！在最後一個敵人的鮮血流盡之前，我們都無法取得真正的勝利！", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#2"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你就沒有想過，你所做的一切，正是我們的敵人想讓你做的？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_227_1"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你擔心的事，恰好是我所希望的——", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我希望這些塔拉人的下場能傳遍整個維多利亞！", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要摧毀的不是這一群人，我要摧毀的是他們的勇氣。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要讓所有人知道，在他們生出反叛之心的時候，都該掂量下自己能否承受住維多利亞的怒火！", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你今天點起來的這把火，要多少無辜者的鮮血才能澆滅？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "心懷鬼胎的大公爵，暗中窺伺的各強鄰，野心勃勃的異族人——", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——那麼多圖謀不軌的人聚在一起，倫蒂尼姆，乃至整個維多利亞，早就承受著超出閾值的壓力。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陰謀家們只等著小小的推力，然後，砰——", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "火勢一旦蔓延，不止會燒到塔拉人身上，到最後，在這片曾經繁華的土地上，無一人能夠倖免。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_227_1"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即便如此......也比沉默著被內部的蛀蟲咬成空殼要好。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來你不可能回頭了。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，我和你，再無話可說。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_227_1"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正好，我也不必再關著你，你想滾就滾。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#7"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你一旦釋放我，我就不會放過你。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#7"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以三角鐵小組的名義起誓——無論後面發生什麼，只要我活著，我一定會把你抓上軍事法庭！", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#7"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_227_1#6"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，你以為我會害怕？", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#6"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽著，斯卡曼德羅斯，如果維多利亞要審判我，我哪裡都不會去。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#6"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我迫不及待地想看到那一天。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorclosequite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大提琴，雙簧管，我們去通訊基地台。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萬一風笛沒能把信使安全地送出城，那我們一定要把握住這唯一的機會。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "目前看來，通訊基地台很可能已經落入敵手。這場仗一定不好打。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，我們從來沒有害怕過。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#7"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前進吧，維多利亞的戰士們！帶上三角鐵他們的份一起！", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#7"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G2_opera_room", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkalley_intro", "key": "$darkalley_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_227_1"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戰況怎麼樣了？", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼沒有回復——希爾？", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_227_1#4"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你不在這裡。你竟然，擅離職守。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#4"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_227_1"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有我的命令，你去了哪裡？！", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G4_victoria_street_d_ruins"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼......傷患真的太多了......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "輕傷的儘量疏散，讓他們去完好的建築裡避難，重症傷患集中送去最近的診所——而且要記得做好隔離。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "診所的床鋪很緊張。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "附近就是塔拉居民聚集的十七區，受到的轟炸最嚴重。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有居民自發清理出了一塊乾淨的區域，搭了幾個帳篷和幾十張床位，充當臨時站點。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您教我的防護方法，我也教了他們，幾位志願者正在把部分不算危重的傷患安置到帳篷裡去。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等我把這裡剩下的急救物資清理完，我就去找他們。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你很擅長幹這些事，他們很容易信任你。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈......這些年在軍營裡，我所學的就是如何討人喜歡。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們告訴我，儀仗兵是軍隊的臉面，我深信不疑，我習慣了他們用掌聲和歡呼歌頌維多利亞的光輝和繁盛。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒人能否認，這的確是維多利亞的一部分。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......但並非全部。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您同我說了那些話以後，我想到了一些被我遺忘的過去的事。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "爸爸是個律師，他就經常跟我講爺爺的爺爺來維多利亞白手起家的故事。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在他的描繪裡，維多利亞是個發達、開明、生機勃勃的國家。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這裡，技術和資本戰勝了蠻荒，人們努力積累的財富，不會輕易地被一場天災或者部族爭鬥摧毀。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正是因為來到了這樣的國度，我們瓦伊凡才有機會不再靠著野蠻的武力生活下去，我們得以過上更“文明”的生活。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#5", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在很長一段時間內，維多利亞無疑代表了大地上最先進的生產力。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#5"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#5", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但為了變得更像一個維多利亞人，我們也放棄了很多......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#5", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "五歲那年，當我為輕鬆爬上花園裡最高的樹而雀躍的時候，爸爸嚴厲地訓斥了我。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他把我關在房間內，給我塞了幾十本書，並在第二天就為我請了一位萊塔尼亞的鋼琴教師。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我那時雖然有些不捨得樹上的風光，可並未多想，我相信爸爸是為了我好。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他在幫助你更好地適應這裡的規則。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊。書本，鋼琴，花園......爸爸比我清楚，要是不適應的話，我們根本沒法擁有這樣的生活。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，我還想到一件事......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一次放學後，我看到我最喜歡的麵包店後面，有幾個高年級的學生正在欺負一個菲林女孩。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們笑話她髒兮兮的衣裳，還笑話她什麼都不懂。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在他們走後，我悄悄地走上前，把我書包裡的幾本小說送給了那個女孩。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以為等她看完了這些故事，她就能和同齡人聊起來，就不會再遭笑話了......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一星期後我興沖沖地去找她，想和她聊聊書裡的內容，結果她搖了搖頭，把書都還給了我。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一眼看出來，這些書她翻都沒有翻開過。我當時很生氣，覺得自己把心愛的書借給了她，想和她交朋友，而她居然一點都不領情。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很久以後，我才知道......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她並不識字。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#5", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "作為麵包店幫傭的孩子，她很難獲得受教育的機會，更不必說和你一樣。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#5"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#5", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來，能讀小說也是一種奢侈。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞從未能做到對所有人一視同仁，對不對？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#5", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "過去的我不願意承認......是我主動適應了“規則”，我才成了一名合格的維多利亞人。而規則之外的人，從來不被維多利亞承認。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能主動醒過來且保持清醒，這本身就需要勇氣。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尤其這個夢是整個群體編織出來的關於某種文明形態的共同想像——相信我，沒有人比我更瞭解。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為您是拉特蘭人？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為我離開了拉特蘭。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有機會的話真想聽您講講過去的事......而不是讓您聽這麼多傻兮兮的普通人的煩惱。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "簡，你並不普通。沒有人該說自己普通。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝，多虧了您一直安慰我，我才沒有耽擱在沒用的情緒裡。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也從未停止努力。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "物資都收拾好了，我這就把它們搬去臨時醫療點。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "路上依然要保持警惕。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，現在城裡亂成一片。好在駐軍停止了攻擊，暴徒也基本被打散了，只要市民們能團結起來，小丘郡還有救。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們遠比想像中的要堅韌。許多野心家低估了這一點，最後輸得很慘。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，最大的問題還是，藥品不太夠用。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先做好清潔和包紮。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我這裡還有藥，你們分給我的，我現在用不上。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是能拿出來一部分，還能多救幾個人。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "收回去。別打這個主意。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "救人之前，先確保自己的安全。這是為了救更多人。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......好，我記住了。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等我送完東西，我就回來找您。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一片傷患處理得差不多了。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那您還要去雕像另一側嗎？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 3.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "name": "avg_npc_012", "style": "cutin", "fadestyle": "horiz_expand_center", "fadetime": 0.5, "width": 200.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女士，我在望遠鏡裡看到，在你前面不遠的街區，還有一個受傷的人躺在地上。", "name": "幹員弗雷德"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#2"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼樣的人？", "name": "Outcast"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#2"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女性，很年輕。看不出種族......大概是瓦伊凡？", "name": "幹員弗雷德"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#2"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "情況怎樣？", "name": "Outcast"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#2"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很不好。看樣子，她的腹部被大塊源石晶簇貫穿了，極大機率已經被感染，目前看來可能失血過多，正處於昏迷狀態。", "name": "幹員弗雷德"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我馬上過去。", "name": "Outcast"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等......女士，我發現那是交戰區！", "name": "幹員弗雷德"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖說目前附近沒什麼敵人，但那一帶之前都被暴徒佔領了，而且，背後那棟建築就是他們的指揮中心！", "name": "幹員弗雷德"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以呢？", "name": "Outcast"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......傷者極有可能是對方的重要人物。", "name": "幹員弗雷德"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們這一路救人不分陣營。", "name": "Outcast"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，我無法判斷......奧利弗先生，你都聽到了嗎？", "name": "幹員弗雷德"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "name": "char_013_riop", "style": "cutin", "fadestyle": "horiz_expand_center", "fadetime": 0.5, "width": 200.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的......女士，我也不贊同貿然行動。這樣一個牽扯眾多的人物，要是真被我們救下了，搞不好會給羅德島帶來巨大的風險。", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白。你們看到的是一個權力鬥爭漩渦中心的人物染上了礦石病。", "name": "Outcast"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我看到的是，一個感染者之後會因權力鬥爭而死。", "name": "Outcast"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，在她真正死去之前，圍繞著她還會有更多的權力鬥爭，更多人會隨之喪命。", "name": "Outcast"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這悲慘的命運降臨之前，只要我有一絲機會阻止，我就不會放棄。", "name": "Outcast"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......女士，我沒法說服你，但我會服從你的指令。", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，奧利弗，我沒有資格命令你，也不想命令你。", "name": "Outcast"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請你記住，並且務必要在任務報告裡寫下來——", "name": "Outcast"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不是羅德島精英幹員的決策。這是我，Outcast，我個人的決定。", "name": "Outcast"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是......", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，也加上你的這些“可是”。", "name": "Outcast"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“臨時幹員Outcast，未遵守地區負責人的撤退命令，一意孤行實施危險人物的救援”——就這麼寫。", "name": "Outcast"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算您這麼說......女士，不考慮羅德島，你繼續前進也會很危險！", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是為什麼我們不能把更多人捲進來。", "name": "Outcast"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "本次行動最好和羅德島沒關係。你和其他幹員按原定計劃行事，等完成救援任務，就立刻帶著資料撤離小丘郡。", "name": "Outcast"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "2", "name": "avg_npc_089", "style": "cutin", "fadestyle": "horiz_expand_center", "fadetime": 0.5, "width": 200.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name2": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......女士，我留下等你。", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name2": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "碎紙機？！", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name2": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧利弗，你要是想的話，報告裡加一句，把我就地開除。", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name2": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說什麼混帳話！", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好......好。你們去吧。不就是救一個感染者嗎？這樣的事，我們羅德島從來幹得不少！", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別想讓我丟下你們任何一個，記得按時來會合點！", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name2": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝。奧利弗，你幹得很出色。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "碎紙機，我也很感激你的幫助。但是，我希望你能聽從我的建議。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就是——留在原地。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前面我一個人去。無論發生什麼，你們都不要管，到時候直接去會合地點就行。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name2": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是，女士。我會準備好接應。", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "2", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Outcast......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "簡，你不會想要拉住我吧？", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你真的要去救那個人嗎？他們說，那人是暴徒裡的重要人物......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她會不會就是殺了西爾莎的兇手？！", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#5", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我想，一個神秘且有野心的組織，很難會放任自己真正的頭領奄奄一息地躺在大街上。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#5"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#5", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼......那就好，我、我心裡舒服多了。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果她是的話，你會怎麼做？你會希望我不要救她嗎？", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說實話，我不知道。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我認同您說的話，她是一名可憐的感染者，急需我們的幫助。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許等她脫離危險，我會問問她......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了，或許是我想多了，我還是不耽誤您的時間了。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我走了。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，還有......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您跟我說過的，救人之前，先確保自己安全！", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽聽，我們的小簡妮也學會反過來教育我了。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我不敢......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#3$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心吧。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像我們說好的——我只是去救一名普通的感染者。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}